          </button>

          <noscript><p class="reg-noscript">完成报名需要启用 JavaScript（人机验证需要它）。如无法启用，请发送邮件至 <a href="mailto:organizers@ebim-benchmark.org">organizers@ebim-benchmark.org</a>。</p></noscript>

        </div>
      </form>

      <div id="formSuccess" class="form-success" role="status" hidden>
